<article id="post-3199" class="post-3199 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-family category-general category-pop-culture tag-christmas tag-evans-hunt tag-movies tag-party tag-shopping tag-zoo">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2012/12/christmas-blitzkrieg/" rel="bookmark">Christmas Blitzkrieg</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>When I have those moments when I think I&#8217;ve gotten too old, and I think I&#8217;m starting to feel like my age, I&#8217;m thankful for sudden sustained bursts of activity that remind me that, really, I just lead a much duller life than I used to, and my exhaustion is usually due to lack of sleep than from trying to do too much.<br />
Heck, it even makes me feel a bit young! Ish. Sort of.<br />
Except for the prolonged yawning, anyway.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2012/12/christmas-blitzkrieg/#more-3199" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Christmas Blitzkrieg&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
