<article id="post-2973" class="post-2973 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-children category-family category-general tag-christmas">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2011/12/merry-christmas-2011/" rel="bookmark">Merry Christmas, 2011</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>It&#8217;s been a long silence, I know. This has been a tough year for the Sowrey family. Between kids growing up, new jobs, and pressures from all angles, finding the time to write is a challenge unlike any I&#8217;ve experienced. And frankly, it becomes a lot lower on my priorities, despite how much I miss it.<br />
That brings me to today, Christmas Day 2011. Today is another long, hard day in a long line of long, hard days. But not a bad day &#8212; certainly not bad. Just long, and by the end of it my head is spinning and I long for a day where I don&#8217;t have to do anything &#8230; despite knowing full well that were I actually to get such a day, I&#8217;d be bored outta my tree.<br />
Such is the life of the working parent, I suppose&#8230;<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2011/12/merry-christmas-2011/#more-2973" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Merry Christmas, 2011&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2011/12/merry-christmas-2011/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2011-12-25T23:50:49-07:00">25 December 2011</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/children/" rel="category tag">Children</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/family/" rel="category tag">Family</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/christmas/" rel="tag">christmas</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2011/12/merry-christmas-2011/#respond">Leave a comment<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Merry Christmas, 2011</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
