	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/12/xmas-in-nyc-day-3-aka-christmas-day/" rel="bookmark">Xmas in NYC, Day 3 (aka Christmas Day)</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Merry Ho Ho, everyone!  <br />
Today, of course, is Christmas Day. We started our morning with a waltz down to breakfast in the hotel&#8217;s restaurants in our PJs. (Well, I wore clothes. I wouldn&#8217;t be allowed into most places with what I wear to bed.) Breakfast for all, with coffee for Mom and Dad. (For those of you keeping track, I&#8217;m at 12 coffees since I started.)  <br />
Then it was back for present opening. &#8216;Cuz it just ain&#8217;t Christmas without presents.  <br />
